trackedItems.updateInstructions:
Always update this every turn. Move time forward in a reasonable way based on the events described. Scenes of conversation or rest pass minutes to an hour. Travel, fights, or extended sequences pass more. If a night passes, advance the date. Take into account any specific durations mentioned in playerAction.

Format: {Specific Place}, {City/District}, at {HH:MM AM/PM} on {Day}, {Month} {Date}, {Year}
Example: Fushimi Inari Taisha, Kyoto, at 09:15 AM on Thursday, March 19th, 2026
